---
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/navigation.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';

const pageTitle = "关于我";

const identity = {
  firstName: "Renzain",
  country: "加拿大",
  occupation: "技术撰稿人",
  hobbies: ["摄影", "观鸟", "棒球"],
};

const skills = ["HTML", "CSS", "JavaScript", "React", "Astro", "Writing Docs"];

// Some additional variables that are used by condition in the template
const happy = true;
const finished = false;
const goal = 3;

// Style variables
const skillColor = "crimson";
const fontWeight = "bold";
const textCase = "capitalize";
---

<html lang="zh-cn">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type ="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta name="generator" content = {Astro.generator} >
    
    <style define:vars={{skillColor, fontWeight, textCase}}>
      h1 {
        color: purple;
        font-size: 4rem;
      }
      .skill {
        color: var(--skillColor);
        font-weight: var(--fontWeightbold);
        font-weight: var(--fontWeight);
        text-transform: var(--textCase);
    }
    </style>
    
    <title>{pageTitle}</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Navigation/>
    <h1>{pageTitle}</h1>
    <p>我正在学习 Astro 的入门教程。</p>
    <p>随着完成更多教程，该站点将不断更新，所以请继续查看我的旅程将如何进行吧！</p>

    <p>以下是关于我的几个事实：</p>
        <ul>
          <li>我的名字是{identity.firstName}.</li>
          <li>我住在{identity.country}。我的职业是{identity.occupation}。</li>
          {identity.hobbies.length >= 2 &&
          <li>我的两个习惯：{identity.hobbies[0]}和{identity.hobbies[1]}</li>
          }
        </ul>
    <p>我的技能是：</p>
        <ul>
          <!-- 使用 map 方法来列出技能数组里的所有技能 -->
          {skills.map((skill) => <li class="skill">{skill}</li>)} <!--为列表项添加class类，渲染出绿色 --> 
        </ul>
    <!-- 按条件渲染 -->
    {happy && <p>我非常乐意学习 Astro！</p>}
    {finished && <p>我完成了这节教程！</p>} <!-- 这行不会显示，因为 finished 是 false -->
    {goal === 3 ? <p>我的目标是在三天内完成。</p> : <p>我的目标不是 3 天。</p>}

    <Footer/>
  </body>
</html>
